article_title: Blue Cross Partners With Google-Backed Startup To Speed Mental Health Referrals

article_metadata.description: Highmark Blue Cross and Blue Shield has partnered with Google Ventures' backed Quartet Health to speed the notoriously slow referral process to psychiatrists from primary care doctors.
article_metadata.author: Bruce Japsen
